title: Sydney Viewing Party & 1v1s a@ First Round Esports Bar
body:
Hello Summoners, 

We will be hosting at viewing party and 1v1 casual tournament at First Round Esport bar. 

Sign ups are between 2-5pm. 

1v1 starting at 5pm. 

Viewing party starting at 7pm. 

We have got swag, skins to give away for the night! 

So come join us! 

Address: 1 The Esplanade, Ashfield NSW 2131, Australia

replies.body: NOOOOOOOOOOO 2 weekends before ranked season finishes :(
